### ============================================================================
### PIPELINE-API-003 | 파이프라인 외부 연동 Webhook 등록
### Markdown source: docs/03_API/PHASE2_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: POST /api/pipeline/{job_id}/webhook
### 관련 기능 ID: PROJECT-PIPELINE-B-203
### 상태: 시작 전 (Phase 2)
### 공통 오류 계약: ../_shared/ERROR-CONTRACT.http
### 변경 이력: PROJECT-PIPELINE-API-003 WebSocket 진행률 계약은 단계 조회
### polling 계약으로 통합. target/payload가 미확정이던 PROJECT-PIPELINE-API-004
### external-sync 초안은 PIPELINE-API-003 Webhook 계약으로 구체화.
### 보안: secret은 응답·로그에 노출하지 않고 저장 시 암호화 또는 secret manager 사용.
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@jobId = a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pipeline/{{jobId}}/webhook
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"webhookUrl":"https://example.com/codemap/events","events":["completed","failed"],"secret":"replace-me-webhook-secret"}

### 201 Created
### {"code":201,"message":"created","data":{"webhookId":"webhook-uuid","webhookUrl":"https://example.com/codemap/events"}}
### events: completed | failed

### [오류] 허용되지 않는 URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pipeline/{{jobId}}/webhook
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"webhookUrl":"file:///etc/passwd","events":["completed"]}

### 400 INVALID_WEBHOOK_URL / 404 JOB_NOT_FOUND
### {"code":400,"message":"Webhook URL 형식이 올바르지 않습니다.","data":null,"error":{"code":"INVALID_WEBHOOK_URL","detail":"Only approved https destinations are allowed","field":"webhookUrl","retryable":false}}
